| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3703 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7c082103-3cbf-52f9-8445-8ee119502977"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
